Wes-Del Community Schools

  · July 10  ·
Wes-Del Community Schools will not require masks to be worn in or on school grounds this upcoming 2021-2022 school year. Students and staff may wear a mask if they choose, but it will not be required. School begins on Monday, August 9th.
